    <div class="gow-row" style="flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start;gap:6px;margin-top:10px">
      <label class="gow-label" for="wolf_network_mode">Wolf network mode</label>
      <select name="wolf_network_mode" id="wolf_network_mode" class="gow-select">
        <option value="host" <?= ($wolf_network_mode === 'host') ? 'selected' : '' ?>>Host</option>
        <option value="bridge" <?= ($wolf_network_mode === 'bridge') ? 'selected' : '' ?>>Bridge</option>
        <option value="custom" <?= ($wolf_network_mode === 'custom') ? 'selected' : '' ?>>Custom Docker network</option>
      </select>
      <p class="gow-help">Bridge publishes Wolf's default Moonlight ports on the host. Use a custom Docker network such as br0 with a static IP when another Sunshine/GameStream server already uses the Unraid host IP.</p>
